Save Time!
USAir's schedules are designed to fit the business
travelers' needs with same-day, out-and-back service
between many cities. An added convenience is the
Allegheny Commuter system, providing frequent,
well-timed service linking smaller and mid-sized
communities to major USAir cities.

group and vacation traveler. Restrictions apply.

USAir offers a 50% discount for all U.S. active duty
personnel and their eligible family dependents-and
dependents are not required to travel with the active
duty member! Call your SATO or USAir.
